quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  17,67,"Si lorra kan he…ďii on ka maayo, majjay …ďen …ďe noddayno …óon, si wonaa Kanko [Alla] nde O danndi on ka njorndi …óurno…óon, ne…ó…óanke on wonii te o seeraani wonde heewu…óo yeddugol"
  17,68,"Enee, on hooli O mutintaa on ka banŇče njorndi maa…óun O nula e mon damagariire [to…ďo koccu], refti hara he…ďantaake on fawtii…óo"
  17,69,"Kaa on hooli O ruttaraa on e maggo laawol goo O accita e dow mon bippooru immorde e keneeli O yoolira on sabu ko yedduno…óon kon, refti on he…ďantaake jokkitiray…óo e dow amen cukkoowo"
  17,70,"Gom…óii, Men teddinii …ďi…ó…ďe Aadama …ďen, Men ronndike …ďe ka njorndi e ka maayo Men arsiki …ďe immorde e laa…ďu…ói Men …ďurni …ďe e dow ko heewi e …ďen …ďe Men tagi …ďurnudee"
  17,71,"√Ďannde Men noddiroyta kala yim…ďe yeesoojo ma…ď…ďe on,kala on jonnitiroyaa…óo deftere makko nden ka √Īaamo makko …ďen …óon …ďe janngay deftere ma…ď…ďe nden …ďe too√Īirtaake hay yeru gaarayol hun tamaro"
  17,72,"Kala on wonu…óo e [ngurndan aduna] ko o bun…óo, haray kanko, ko ka laahara o …ďurata wumude e majjude laawol"
  17,73,"Fii kala …ďe e…ď…ďii nde …ďe fitinaymaa gaayi nden huunde nde Men wahayini e maa…óa fii yo a fefindo e Amen ko wonaa …óun [ko Men tellini e maa] ontuma …ďe jogitoto ma sehlaajo"
  17,74,"Si tawiino Men tabintinaanoma, gom…óii hari a do'ii oo√Īaade e ma…ď…ďe huunde see…óaare"
  17,75,"Ontuma Men mee…óinteno cowale [lepte] ka ngurndan e cowale [lepte] ka mayde refti he…ďantaake ma ballo e hoore Amen"
